WEBVTT

01:51.880 --> 01:55.680
This drought looks
even worse than I expected.

01:56.280 --> 01:58.520
Right. The shops are all closed,

01:59.040 --> 02:01.520
and the townsfolk can barely get by.

02:02.120 --> 02:04.160
There's demonic energy
from Han Ba everywhere.

02:05.800 --> 02:07.480
He really is clever,

02:08.360 --> 02:10.560
spreading his demonic energy
all over the city.

02:11.080 --> 02:13.720
Now it's impossible to pin down
his exact location.

02:15.120 --> 02:16.200
Bai Ze said

02:16.720 --> 02:18.480
that as soon as Han Ba spoke,

02:19.000 --> 02:21.160
the searing heat inside him would escape

02:21.240 --> 02:22.680
and bring drought upon the land.

02:23.680 --> 02:25.560
That's why he always kept his mouth shut

02:25.640 --> 02:26.800
and cultivated alone.

02:29.080 --> 02:30.880
Judging by the scale of this drought,

02:31.760 --> 02:35.040
Han Ba's probably
turned into a chatterbox by now.

02:36.120 --> 02:40.280
By the way, did you tell You Chi
about Ji Ling?

02:41.000 --> 02:42.520
-Mother…
-Not yet.

02:42.600 --> 02:43.640
I'm hungry.

02:43.720 --> 02:46.040
I'm worried that if he finds out,

02:46.720 --> 02:49.400
every weasel in the streets will know too.

02:49.920 --> 02:51.840
That'll be no different
from posting notices all over the city.

02:59.640 --> 03:02.040
See? We've only been apart for a while,

03:02.120 --> 03:03.760
and Wu Shiguang already misses me.

03:05.640 --> 03:07.520
Obviously, Wu Shiguang
has ditched his friend

03:08.040 --> 03:09.280
now that he has a loved one.

03:09.800 --> 03:11.400
Why else did he dump you on me?

03:11.920 --> 03:13.200
Nonsense.

03:13.720 --> 03:15.400
I'm the unlucky one here,

03:16.160 --> 03:18.680
getting stuck with a scary brute like you

03:18.760 --> 03:20.280
to look for a place to stay.

03:21.640 --> 03:23.160
Look at this fierce face of yours.

03:24.760 --> 03:27.880
Even if we find an inn,
they might not dare take us in.

03:29.520 --> 03:31.480
-Have you heard of a saying?
-What saying?

03:33.080 --> 03:34.080
Weasel, meet your maker.

03:45.480 --> 03:47.000
There's not a soul in sight.

03:47.520 --> 03:49.200
How are we supposed
to find a place to stay?

03:49.280 --> 03:50.600
Let's look around first.

03:56.640 --> 03:57.560
Here.

04:01.320 --> 04:02.400
What,

04:03.800 --> 04:04.840
you don't like it anymore?

04:07.640 --> 04:09.720
It doesn't really go
with what I'm wearing today.

04:10.720 --> 04:12.000
And you think

04:12.720 --> 04:14.040
it goes well with me?

04:15.320 --> 04:17.040
Just hold it.

04:18.519 --> 04:21.480
Besides, I haven't seen
Ji Ling in a very long time.

04:23.640 --> 04:25.720
Ji Ling…

04:26.240 --> 04:27.920
-All you ever talk about is Ji Ling.
-Ji.

04:33.840 --> 04:35.760
Don't call me that
in front of the others later.

04:36.400 --> 04:37.240
You don't like it?

04:37.840 --> 04:40.200
It's not that. It makes me sound
like some half-grown kid.

04:40.800 --> 04:41.960
But it's cute.

04:45.080 --> 04:47.520
Fine. Call me whatever you like.

04:48.720 --> 04:50.920
Fair's fair.

04:51.000 --> 04:52.320
From now on, Ji, you can call me Wu too.

04:52.920 --> 04:54.000
Wu?

04:54.520 --> 04:55.800
Like the sound a fox makes?

04:55.880 --> 04:57.080
Awoo!

04:57.600 --> 04:59.840
Its name is Wu.

04:59.920 --> 05:01.760
Sorry, but the name's been taken.

05:02.440 --> 05:03.280
Master Dragon Deity,

05:03.960 --> 05:05.800
that kind of joke doesn't really suit you.

05:07.280 --> 05:08.360
Cut it out.

05:15.480 --> 05:18.480
Did Jiu Ying give you a hard time
back in the Formless Moon?

05:20.720 --> 05:21.960
I'm fine.

05:22.480 --> 05:23.800
On the other hand,

05:23.880 --> 05:26.200
you used to be
at each other's throats with Ji Ling,

05:26.280 --> 05:28.080
but now you two
are getting along pretty well.

05:31.120 --> 05:32.440
A hundred years on the divine throne,

05:32.960 --> 05:34.320
walking on thin ice,

05:35.240 --> 05:36.960
pretending to be someone else,

05:37.920 --> 05:39.280
and living like a shadow,

05:40.160 --> 05:41.640
never able to speak the truth,

05:43.600 --> 05:44.960
he doesn't have it easy.

05:46.560 --> 05:48.240
He lived in loneliness for a century.

05:49.680 --> 05:51.480
But now that he's met Wuyi,

05:52.160 --> 05:53.680
he's got some youthful spirit back.

05:53.760 --> 05:56.360
Even the way he dresses
has gotten younger.

05:56.440 --> 05:59.440
Wouldn't you call that an old tree
coming back into bloom?

06:00.480 --> 06:03.680
You and Lu Wuyi
are both thousand-year-old foxes.

06:03.760 --> 06:05.360
Compared to you two,

06:05.960 --> 06:08.520
Ji Ling and I are the tender shoots.

06:10.160 --> 06:12.280
You're siding with him already?

06:13.680 --> 06:15.960
People always say
fox demons are heartless,

06:16.640 --> 06:20.120
but Wuyi takes love

06:20.200 --> 06:21.800
more seriously than anything.

06:21.880 --> 06:24.880
It's a blessing
that he's won Wuyi's heart.

06:25.400 --> 06:28.080
Even if it comes with misfortune,
he should accept it without complaint.

06:28.880 --> 06:30.000
Then what about you?

06:36.360 --> 06:37.640
You're a fox demon too.

06:41.080 --> 06:42.160
Where's your heart?

06:57.520 --> 06:58.720
Vacant rooms!

06:58.800 --> 07:01.120
Clean and comfortable rooms
at fair prices!

07:01.200 --> 07:03.680
Don't miss out!

07:04.200 --> 07:06.760
A desert oasis
and a spring in the wasteland.

07:06.840 --> 07:07.960
-this is the perfect haven for travelers!
-With the whole city this desolate,

07:08.040 --> 07:09.600
someone's still drumming up business
for an inn?

07:09.680 --> 07:11.360
It's definitely a trap.

07:25.120 --> 07:26.440
A trap?

07:27.320 --> 07:29.400
The inn is brightly lit
and spotlessly clean.

07:29.480 --> 07:30.560
Don't go throwing that word around.

07:31.400 --> 07:33.880
Times are unusual right now,
so we're running a special promotion.

07:33.960 --> 07:35.680
We're collecting curious stories
from ordinary folk.

07:35.760 --> 07:38.280
If you two can offer us a good one,

07:39.040 --> 07:40.840
your stay is on the house.

07:40.920 --> 07:42.240
On the house?

07:43.880 --> 07:44.720
That sounds good.

07:45.320 --> 07:48.000
-Where's your inn? Is it far?
-Not far at all.

07:48.080 --> 07:49.520
It's right here.

07:49.600 --> 07:51.360
CHATTER INN

07:52.000 --> 07:53.400
-Wangyan!
-Wuyi.

07:53.480 --> 07:54.880
You're here too?

08:05.600 --> 08:07.120
What's going on?

08:08.520 --> 08:09.520
I scared him.

08:12.800 --> 08:15.160
Ji's all fair and pretty.
How could he have scared anyone?

08:17.120 --> 08:18.600
Didn't we agree you wouldn't call me Ji?

08:18.680 --> 08:20.600
What's wrong, Ji?

08:20.680 --> 08:22.200
Ji?

08:24.400 --> 08:27.720
It seems the innkeeper knows Ji Ling.

08:29.800 --> 08:31.400
Of course he does.

08:31.480 --> 08:34.760
He is Han Ba.

08:38.880 --> 08:40.120
Is that so? Ji…

08:47.440 --> 08:48.600
I'm exhausted.

08:49.720 --> 08:50.920
I can't do this anymore.

08:51.440 --> 08:52.400
I can't.

08:52.920 --> 08:54.040
My legs are about to give out.

08:54.920 --> 08:56.160
You go find an inn.

08:56.960 --> 08:58.640
I'll just curl up
in some hole by the road.

08:58.720 --> 09:00.880
-No way.
-Then carry me.

09:08.320 --> 09:09.520
Listen.

09:10.040 --> 09:11.360
Walk on your own. I'm not carrying you.

09:11.440 --> 09:12.880
What?

09:12.960 --> 09:14.600
Listen. Don't turn around.

09:15.160 --> 09:19.160
There's a girl following me
and sneaking looks at me.

09:20.600 --> 09:21.640
Hey!

09:21.720 --> 09:23.360
Get back here. What are you doing?

09:24.480 --> 09:25.800
She's following me.

09:26.560 --> 09:27.440
What nonsense.

09:27.520 --> 09:29.080
She's not blind.

09:29.160 --> 09:32.280
It's obvious which of us is more handsome.

09:34.520 --> 09:36.440
Miss, I'm You…

09:36.520 --> 09:40.120
Are you the one who used to be
by Master Chi Wen's side?

09:42.400 --> 09:43.760
I'm Li Jie.

09:44.920 --> 09:47.080
Do… Do you still remember me?

09:53.040 --> 09:54.760
<i>Master Chi Wen,</i>

09:54.840 --> 09:58.160
<i>please… please watch</i>
<i>over my great-grandmother.</i>

09:58.240 --> 10:02.360
<i>Please let her get better soon.</i>

10:17.200 --> 10:21.640
Please… please let her recover quickly.

10:23.520 --> 10:24.360
Please.

10:29.400 --> 10:31.240
Master Chi Wen sent me
to pass a message on to you.

10:32.600 --> 10:34.000
Your long vigil and prayers here

10:34.600 --> 10:36.480
show a devotion
heaven and earth can witness.

10:36.560 --> 10:38.240
But birth, aging, sickness, and death

10:38.320 --> 10:39.960
are the ways of the world.

10:40.560 --> 10:43.160
Every mortal life has its end.

10:44.480 --> 10:45.440
The Dragon Deity's Power

10:46.160 --> 10:48.440
cannot be used
to reverse the laws of nature.

10:51.360 --> 10:52.960
Instead of wasting your time

10:53.640 --> 10:55.080
kneeling here in prayer,

10:55.840 --> 10:57.480
you should spend
more time with your family

10:58.080 --> 10:59.520
and cherish the days you have.

11:00.600 --> 11:02.640
Does the Master Dragon Deity know

11:03.440 --> 11:05.680
about all the suffering in this world?

11:08.800 --> 11:09.640
He does.

11:11.600 --> 11:13.480
Then does he just ignore it all?

11:15.960 --> 11:17.560
Master Dragon Deity said

11:19.360 --> 11:23.280
what carries us through suffering
and helps us overcome evil

11:24.320 --> 11:25.960
is not the protection of the gods,

11:26.800 --> 11:28.240
but the hope and courage

11:28.760 --> 11:30.440
that never fade

11:31.480 --> 11:32.880
from our hearts.

11:39.800 --> 11:42.040
He asked me to return this to you.

11:50.000 --> 11:52.320
Do you remember this?

11:55.240 --> 11:56.320
I do.

11:58.960 --> 12:00.400
Master Dragon Deity,

12:01.000 --> 12:03.120
have you come to take back
the Dragon Deity's Power?

12:04.960 --> 12:08.360
And you're telling me
this man is a dragon,

12:09.920 --> 12:13.160
and these two are foxes
over 1,000 years old?

12:13.880 --> 12:16.560
This is too much for me.

12:16.640 --> 12:19.720
I only wanted to run a small business
and keep an inn.

12:19.800 --> 12:24.680
Why send such a force to come after me?

12:24.760 --> 12:27.120
Luo'an is parched with drought.
Why do you think?

12:27.200 --> 12:28.800
Why did you run into the inn and hide?

12:29.800 --> 12:32.280
Did you think that door would keep me out?

12:32.360 --> 12:33.880
Why's the inn door busted?

12:33.960 --> 12:36.560
Did some bandit barge in
and start looting and killing?

12:36.640 --> 12:38.960
Don't be scared. I'll take care of them!

12:42.080 --> 12:43.520
You're all here?

12:44.360 --> 12:45.520
You beat us again.

12:55.320 --> 12:57.680
My eyes are quite alluring.

13:06.160 --> 13:08.560
What are you all doing?
Why is the mood so tense?

13:09.160 --> 13:10.000
Forcing…

13:13.280 --> 13:15.440
asking someone to hand
over the Dragon Deity's Power.

13:17.520 --> 13:21.680
Are you afraid that once
you hand it over, you'll die?

13:26.800 --> 13:29.400
These extra years I've lived,
propped up by the Dragon Deity's Power,

13:29.480 --> 13:31.600
were stolen to begin with.

13:32.560 --> 13:33.880
I'm not afraid of dying.

13:35.560 --> 13:37.120
What I'm afraid of

13:39.120 --> 13:41.040
is that once I hand over
the Dragon Deity's Power,

13:41.640 --> 13:44.360
the searing heat inside me
will spiral out of control,

13:45.360 --> 13:46.800
and drought will break out

13:49.240 --> 13:50.840
across the whole world.

13:52.120 --> 13:53.920
Once we gather
all of the Dragon Deity's Power,

13:55.320 --> 13:58.200
he can become a true dragon,
summon wind and rain,

13:58.720 --> 13:59.840
and end the drought.

14:01.440 --> 14:02.480
Helping him become a dragon

14:03.080 --> 14:04.480
was also Master Chi Wen's wish.

14:05.440 --> 14:06.480
Master Chi Wen?

14:06.560 --> 14:09.920
Is everyone talking about
themselves in the third person now?

14:11.560 --> 14:14.080
So you're the Tenth Dragon Son
we've all been waiting for?

14:15.320 --> 14:16.160
That's right.

14:18.840 --> 14:20.680
What is it? Don't I look the part?

14:20.760 --> 14:22.160
I wouldn't dare say that.

14:23.000 --> 14:24.440
I just didn't expect

14:24.520 --> 14:26.600
the Tenth Dragon Son
to look so utterly ordinary.

14:26.680 --> 14:27.960
You've hidden it well.

14:29.760 --> 14:31.560
See? I told you.

14:32.120 --> 14:33.800
You should've bought some nicer outfits.

14:34.320 --> 14:36.480
Look at Ji Ling. He dresses
so flamboyantly every day.

14:37.600 --> 14:38.920
I heard that.

14:39.000 --> 14:40.440
Both of my ears heard every word.

14:44.800 --> 14:46.160
These past years,

14:47.000 --> 14:49.000
my injuries have only worsened.

14:49.960 --> 14:51.920
The only thing that can suppress

14:52.000 --> 14:53.640
the searing heat inside me
is the Dragon Deity's Power.

14:54.640 --> 14:57.040
I didn't take back my power
to break the oath,

14:57.840 --> 14:59.480
but to suppress the searing heat.

15:02.040 --> 15:03.480
Are your injuries

15:04.360 --> 15:06.120
really incurable?

15:10.720 --> 15:11.560
That's why

15:12.880 --> 15:14.240
this drought befell Luo'an.

15:15.640 --> 15:17.080
I see.

15:17.160 --> 15:19.200
But Luo'an was doomed to drought.

15:19.280 --> 15:20.800
Even if you had kept your mouth shut,

15:20.880 --> 15:22.560
it wouldn't have changed anything.

15:24.720 --> 15:26.280
I only started talking

15:27.320 --> 15:29.920
to fulfill a young girl's wish.

16:22.680 --> 16:24.080
She's the girl I was talking about.

16:25.280 --> 16:26.600
Her name is Mu Long.

16:28.360 --> 16:31.760
These are all stories she and I collected
by waiving lodging fees.

16:32.400 --> 16:35.000
I want to help Mu Long
finish her story collection.

16:35.080 --> 16:37.280
All that's missing now is an ending.

16:39.360 --> 16:41.680
I've watched Mu Long grow up.

16:42.320 --> 16:44.480
Since childhood, she's had a stutter,
kept to herself,

16:44.560 --> 16:45.920
and struggled to get along with people.

16:46.560 --> 16:48.080
The only thing that can make her speak

16:48.680 --> 16:50.920
is when it concerns
this collection of stories.

16:52.280 --> 16:53.920
I have to help her finish it.

16:57.000 --> 16:59.360
Masters and madams,
please give me one more day.

16:59.440 --> 17:00.800
Just one more day.

17:01.720 --> 17:05.040
Tomorrow, I will return
the Dragon Deity's Power.

17:15.359 --> 17:16.400
Do you…

17:16.480 --> 17:18.160
Do you really have good stories?

17:26.839 --> 17:28.040
All right!

17:28.119 --> 17:30.960
Based on how good your stories were,

17:31.040 --> 17:32.960
I've assigned your rooms.

17:33.040 --> 17:34.840
From the most luxurious
to the most modest,

17:34.920 --> 17:38.600
they're divided into Heaven, Earth,
and Human tiers.

17:38.680 --> 17:41.320
Sleep well, everyone.

17:55.360 --> 17:58.600
Han Ba, how dare you put
Master Dragon Deity in a Human-tier room?

18:12.080 --> 18:12.920
An Earth-tier room?

18:13.560 --> 18:14.680
Got a problem?

18:21.360 --> 18:22.760
-We need two rooms.
-Yes.

18:46.280 --> 18:48.080
As I recall,

18:48.160 --> 18:50.200
this lady didn't tell a story just now.

18:50.800 --> 18:52.640
Are you planning to sleep
on the street tonight?

18:53.920 --> 18:56.800
I only tell my stories to the one I love.

18:58.600 --> 19:00.800
Go on. I don't mind
being the one you love.

19:03.280 --> 19:04.560
But I do.

19:05.080 --> 19:06.360
I already have someone I love.

19:07.240 --> 19:08.760
He is the one I love,

19:09.520 --> 19:10.640
and that's settled for life.

19:12.040 --> 19:14.160
I already have someone I love.

19:14.240 --> 19:17.600
He is the one I love,
and that's settled for life.

19:22.920 --> 19:25.720
Then the most comfortable
Heaven-tier suite belongs to you.

19:29.280 --> 19:30.480
Thank you, sir.

19:39.600 --> 19:40.640
Here.

19:41.840 --> 19:43.400
I don't accept charity.

19:45.800 --> 19:47.120
Drop the act.

19:48.080 --> 19:49.640
Could you show me some respect?

19:52.120 --> 19:53.360
Hey you!

20:17.880 --> 20:19.120
What are you doing?

20:19.920 --> 20:23.080
Someone's unhappy. I need to cheer him up.

20:24.800 --> 20:25.640
I'm good.

20:29.280 --> 20:30.480
Why are you being petty?

20:31.160 --> 20:32.840
I am broad-minded.

20:33.560 --> 20:35.640
I just think this wine tastes

20:37.760 --> 20:38.600
very sour.

20:40.880 --> 20:42.040
Sour?

20:45.360 --> 20:46.240
How is it sour?

20:46.320 --> 20:47.560
You're way sourer.

20:49.120 --> 20:51.360
Well? Is it sweet?

20:52.680 --> 20:53.560
It is.

20:56.520 --> 20:57.760
I think it's sweet too.

21:00.840 --> 21:02.080
A Heaven-tier room.

21:06.200 --> 21:09.640
Yunjin brocade, silk bedding, and incense.

21:10.960 --> 21:12.160
Who would've thought

21:12.680 --> 21:15.000
that gaudy, flashy stuff like this

21:15.520 --> 21:17.280
would be enough to make you so happy?

21:20.880 --> 21:23.200
Back at the Shilin Sect,

21:23.280 --> 21:25.600
someone prepared all this for me too.

21:25.680 --> 21:26.520
Who was it?

21:31.320 --> 21:33.640
And I remember someone saying…

21:33.720 --> 21:35.280
-I don't accept charity.
-<i>I don't accept charity.</i>

21:35.920 --> 21:38.040
Don't think you can wear down my resolve

21:39.400 --> 21:41.480
-<i>…with fine clothes and good food.</i>
-with fine clothes and good food.

21:42.720 --> 21:43.960
Who was that?

21:45.240 --> 21:46.720
Why do you know everything?

21:47.840 --> 21:50.400
Does everyone in the Shilin Sect
have special sight and hearing?

21:51.840 --> 21:52.960
Take a guess.

21:54.640 --> 21:55.880
Take a guess?

21:59.000 --> 22:00.080
You tell me.

22:01.320 --> 22:02.240
Are you going to tell me or not?

22:03.960 --> 22:05.400
It won't tell me.

22:06.840 --> 22:07.760
Then don't force it.

22:08.720 --> 22:09.920
Then you tell me.

22:10.000 --> 22:12.280
Then go on and ask it.
I don't remember either.

22:13.520 --> 22:14.680
Tell me!

22:15.200 --> 22:17.480
Yes, you. Say it!

23:57.720 --> 23:59.280
May I have a look?

24:00.160 --> 24:03.720
No. Not even Mr. Yan
has read any of these.

24:03.800 --> 24:07.400
No one gets to read my stories
until I've finished all of them.

24:10.600 --> 24:12.600
Why do you like writing stories?

24:13.720 --> 24:17.600
My great-grandmother used
to tell me stories all the time.

24:18.680 --> 24:21.320
She… She always said
that since I stuttered,

24:21.400 --> 24:25.120
writing stories suited me better.

24:26.440 --> 24:27.880
Too bad

24:28.400 --> 24:31.000
she… she'll never get to read them.

24:34.000 --> 24:37.160
Everything in this world
fades away eventually.

24:37.240 --> 24:39.080
But there's a saying,

24:39.760 --> 24:42.600
"Writers never truly die."

24:43.240 --> 24:44.480
As long as their stories are read,

24:45.160 --> 24:48.320
the days they wrote down
can be relived again.

24:49.600 --> 24:51.720
Your great-grandmother
must be in your stories, right?

24:52.240 --> 24:55.240
Then she will always exist in this world.

24:56.840 --> 24:59.200
She said that too.

24:59.280 --> 25:02.840
Stories can weave the wishes

25:03.560 --> 25:06.040
people dare not speak of

25:06.560 --> 25:09.120
and their regrets

25:09.760 --> 25:12.760
into dreams of fiction.

25:12.840 --> 25:14.440
The people in stories

25:14.960 --> 25:16.560
never die.

25:17.080 --> 25:18.200
I wonder whether my regret

25:20.280 --> 25:21.760
will ever have a happy ending.

25:25.880 --> 25:26.920
Here, Miss Mu.

25:27.560 --> 25:29.080
Th… Thank you.

25:32.640 --> 25:34.640
Your regret?

25:35.160 --> 25:36.960
Do… Do you mean

25:37.040 --> 25:39.080
the girl in your story today,

25:39.600 --> 25:41.960
the one who made you a bracelet?

25:47.920 --> 25:49.000
Yes.

25:49.520 --> 25:50.600
It's a pity.

25:51.720 --> 25:53.240
My bracelet broke.

25:54.360 --> 25:55.640
I'm waiting for her.

25:56.280 --> 25:57.560
And I hope that one day,

25:58.120 --> 26:00.760
she'll be willing
to make me another bracelet.

26:02.960 --> 26:05.400
No… No, that's not right.

26:06.560 --> 26:07.760
Why not?

26:10.040 --> 26:13.200
Because this is your story.

26:13.280 --> 26:14.560
You… You can't just wait.

26:14.640 --> 26:18.480
You need to write it yourself
to get the ending you want.

26:19.480 --> 26:23.120
You… You can make a bracelet yourself.

27:25.320 --> 27:28.560
Ji Ling, you've really got a petty streak.

27:29.320 --> 27:32.400
I shared good food and wine with you,
and you're still ignoring me.

28:21.880 --> 28:23.800
Big drumstick. Big drumstick.

28:23.880 --> 28:25.280
Big drumstick.

28:26.920 --> 28:28.000
Miss Mu?

28:29.720 --> 28:31.000
She's asleep.

28:36.480 --> 28:37.600
Let me take a look.

28:43.920 --> 28:46.400
"The Great Demon and Little Pomegranate."

28:46.480 --> 28:47.560
What kind of writing is this?

28:48.120 --> 28:49.120
It's so ugly.

28:53.080 --> 28:56.000
-Miss Mu Long…
-What are you doing? You…

28:56.080 --> 28:58.960
-You've stained my manuscript!
-I'm sorry.

28:59.040 --> 29:00.200
I forgot my hands were covered in grease.

29:00.280 --> 29:01.160
Don't worry…

29:02.480 --> 29:04.040
Hey, don't cry.

29:04.120 --> 29:06.240
I know. I'll go find Wangyan.

29:06.320 --> 29:08.600
She knows magic.
I'll go get her right now.

29:08.680 --> 29:11.040
Wangyan! Help, Wangyan!

29:11.120 --> 29:13.240
Wangyan, where are you?

29:13.760 --> 29:16.280
Wangyan, help! Wangyan!

29:16.800 --> 29:17.920
Wangyan!

29:19.480 --> 29:20.400
Wangyan!

29:24.280 --> 29:25.400
Wangyan!

29:40.000 --> 29:41.240
Wangyan…

30:01.720 --> 30:02.920
Ji Ling,

30:03.440 --> 30:05.200
why did you do this?

30:10.440 --> 30:12.080
You can go kill Chi Wen now.

30:35.760 --> 30:37.000
Wu Shiguang is under Jiu Ying's control.

30:39.240 --> 30:41.440
You really did keep your promise.

30:42.200 --> 30:43.800
Now you can sit

30:45.120 --> 30:49.000
on the Dragon Deity's throne forever.

30:54.800 --> 30:56.560
You killed my sister.

30:58.560 --> 31:00.480
I'll never forgive you.

31:17.200 --> 31:18.320
It was a dream.

31:29.040 --> 31:30.200
Mu Long.

31:40.880 --> 31:41.720
How?

31:54.760 --> 31:56.320
Not even the Dragon Deity's Power could…

31:56.400 --> 31:57.640
This person doesn't seem to fear magic.

32:10.560 --> 32:11.760
Who was that?

32:11.840 --> 32:13.360
Why did they know my bladework so well?

32:13.440 --> 32:14.720
They didn't know it,

32:15.240 --> 32:16.880
but they could predict
every strike you made.

32:17.520 --> 32:18.560
What in the world is going on?

32:20.440 --> 32:21.560
There's only

32:22.400 --> 32:23.840
one person I know

32:25.480 --> 32:26.600
who's capable of that.

32:30.840 --> 32:31.720
Where are Ji Ling and Lu Wuyi?

32:35.360 --> 32:36.480
Master Dragon Deity.

32:37.720 --> 32:38.840
Master Dragon Deity?

32:54.200 --> 32:55.160
Wuyi.

32:55.800 --> 32:56.800
Wuyi?

33:01.320 --> 33:02.440
Master Dragon Deity isn't in his room.

33:04.520 --> 33:05.360
Is Lu Wuyi gone too?

33:14.560 --> 33:16.640
Li Jie, what are you doing?

33:28.680 --> 33:30.120
Were you two

33:30.640 --> 33:32.240
in the room the whole time?

33:32.800 --> 33:33.720
Wangyan…

34:02.600 --> 34:03.640
Wu,

34:04.960 --> 34:06.800
what in the world is going on?

34:09.159 --> 34:10.520
What are you trying to do?

34:20.560 --> 34:21.440
Mu Long?

34:23.199 --> 34:24.159
Mu Long?

34:31.960 --> 34:34.159
If Mu Long can't go back to normal,

34:35.880 --> 34:37.679
none of you are getting
the Dragon Deity's Power.

34:38.719 --> 34:40.239
Are you threatening us?

34:41.000 --> 34:41.960
I know.

34:42.480 --> 34:43.880
There's no way I can beat

34:44.400 --> 34:46.719
two foxes from the Formless Moon
and two dragons.

34:47.719 --> 34:50.520
But I've already hidden away
the Dragon Deity's Power.

34:51.320 --> 34:52.520
If you don't save Mu Long…

34:53.239 --> 34:54.560
We will.

34:57.880 --> 34:59.000
I can try.

35:00.200 --> 35:01.760
She's under Word Magic.

35:12.880 --> 35:13.840
Master Dragon Deity,

35:13.920 --> 35:15.600
a person in black
attacked Mu Long just now.

35:21.120 --> 35:24.040
Go investigate with Wu Shiguang
and the others.

35:25.320 --> 35:26.400
What about you?

35:26.920 --> 35:28.040
Don't you need me with you?

35:29.760 --> 35:31.600
I have something more important to do.

35:34.760 --> 35:35.720
Understood.

35:57.080 --> 35:59.640
I can't wake her.

36:02.480 --> 36:05.280
Whoever cast the spell
is stronger than I am.

36:05.360 --> 36:07.200
But Word Magic
is the Formless Moon's specialty.

36:07.280 --> 36:08.520
Besides someone from the Formless Moon,

36:08.600 --> 36:10.320
who would know this spell?

36:12.920 --> 36:13.880
Xiaowei.

36:14.520 --> 36:15.600
Xiaowei?

36:17.000 --> 36:18.120
You mean Ji Ling?

36:18.720 --> 36:20.720
How dare you suspect Master Dragon Deity?

36:23.920 --> 36:26.400
He can use Xiaowei's spells
through his Spirit-Binding Ring.

36:26.480 --> 36:27.760
Of course I suspect him.

36:27.840 --> 36:29.840
But didn't you just say

36:30.640 --> 36:32.080
Ji Ling was with your sister?

36:33.600 --> 36:36.560
Maybe Wuyi was helping
Ji Ling cover it up.

36:37.320 --> 36:39.440
With all that fighting
in the front courtyard,

36:39.520 --> 36:40.720
how could the Dragon Deity

36:40.800 --> 36:42.680
not have heard anything?

36:44.360 --> 36:47.440
Wangyan, why do you suspect
Ji Ling so much?

36:48.360 --> 36:49.680
Do you know something?

36:56.920 --> 36:58.080
No.

36:58.920 --> 37:01.240
I just think the person in black
was too strong.

37:01.840 --> 37:03.160
Even together, we couldn't beat them.

37:04.400 --> 37:06.640
Commander Li, aside from Ji Ling,

37:06.720 --> 37:09.000
who else knows your bladework that well?

37:19.840 --> 37:21.640
Why don't you suspect Lu Wuyi?

37:25.160 --> 37:27.680
<i>You said she was covering up for Ji Ling.</i>

37:28.200 --> 37:29.760
<i>Why couldn't it be Ji Ling</i>
<i>covering for her instead?</i>

37:33.200 --> 37:34.200
You also said to me…

37:34.280 --> 37:35.120
There's only

37:35.800 --> 37:37.040
one person I know

37:38.640 --> 37:39.760
who's capable of that.

37:41.000 --> 37:42.480
Were you referring

37:43.880 --> 37:45.440
to Lu Wuyi?

37:47.920 --> 37:50.640
Listen. Is it possible

37:51.640 --> 37:53.720
that both of you are wrong?

37:54.520 --> 37:55.720
What if the two of them
were working together

37:56.840 --> 37:58.720
and covering for each other?

38:01.800 --> 38:04.000
What secret is hidden
in the first chapter of this manuscript?

38:04.800 --> 38:06.960
Why would the person in black
go to such lengths over it?

38:10.160 --> 38:11.520
I haven't read it either.

38:12.240 --> 38:15.280
Mu Long said no one was allowed
to read it until it was finished.

38:17.560 --> 38:19.200
Maybe it has something
to do with my memories.

38:22.880 --> 38:24.480
Do you know me?

38:31.320 --> 38:32.960
So you're finally willing
to talk about this.

38:34.040 --> 38:35.600
I thought you were pretending
not to know me

38:36.640 --> 38:38.320
because there was something
you couldn't say.

38:38.960 --> 38:40.680
I even played along with you.

38:44.600 --> 38:45.840
You really don't remember?

38:48.080 --> 38:50.240
Jiu Ying tampered with my memories.

38:50.320 --> 38:53.120
Any memories I had of you are gone.

38:55.360 --> 38:56.560
Little Pomegranate…

38:58.040 --> 38:59.640
Little Pomegranate…

39:00.440 --> 39:01.920
Little Pomegranate?

39:02.000 --> 39:03.080
What did Miss Mu say?

39:05.240 --> 39:06.880
Little Pomegranate?

39:08.720 --> 39:10.160
-What was it again?
-What,

39:10.680 --> 39:11.920
itching for a beating again?

39:12.520 --> 39:13.440
Want me to scratch you with my blade?

39:13.520 --> 39:14.840
Be quiet.

39:15.360 --> 39:16.760
I'm almost remembering it.

39:18.880 --> 39:20.520
Let me show you a place.

39:20.600 --> 39:23.360
Maybe it will clear things up.

39:25.360 --> 39:26.480
And maybe

39:27.280 --> 39:28.600
it'll help you remember something too.

39:52.120 --> 39:53.520
Thank you.

39:59.600 --> 40:00.880
<i>Sister, higher.</i>

40:01.920 --> 40:04.000
Sister, higher!

40:11.400 --> 40:12.520
What is it?

40:14.880 --> 40:15.880
Nothing.

40:36.600 --> 40:38.880
This used to be
Mu Long's great-grandmother's home,

40:39.520 --> 40:41.280
where she lived as a child.

40:43.920 --> 40:45.120
Where she lived?

40:49.160 --> 40:50.200
I remember now!

40:50.280 --> 40:51.360
You scared me.

40:51.440 --> 40:53.440
The manuscript!
The first chapter of that manuscript

40:54.040 --> 40:55.480
was Little Pomegranate's story.

40:56.000 --> 40:58.040
The moment I heard the words
"Little Pomegranate",

40:58.560 --> 41:01.120
I felt like I'd seen them
somewhere before.

41:02.200 --> 41:04.680
"The Great Demon and Little Pomegranate."

41:04.760 --> 41:06.080
What kind of writing is this?

41:06.160 --> 41:07.120
It's so ugly.

41:07.640 --> 41:10.640
The handwriting was all crooked.
It was ugly.

41:12.440 --> 41:13.440
Really ugly.

41:14.560 --> 41:16.440
But still, I recognized the words
"Little" and "Pomegranate".

41:17.080 --> 41:18.000
But

41:18.680 --> 41:20.080
Mu Long's handwriting is very neat.

41:20.160 --> 41:21.400
How could it be crooked?

41:22.440 --> 41:23.680
She had too much to drink.

41:23.760 --> 41:25.040
Shut it.

41:48.760 --> 41:51.080
Little Pomegranate.

41:57.680 --> 41:58.880
Little Pomegranate?

41:58.960 --> 42:01.160
Why does Little Pomegranate
look like she's crying?

42:05.400 --> 42:06.800
Isn't that Wangyan?

42:16.280 --> 42:17.320
This…

42:18.280 --> 42:19.440
This really is me.

42:21.360 --> 42:23.440
But why would I be in this painting?

42:24.560 --> 42:26.840
And that tall, handsome fellow in the back

42:27.600 --> 42:28.520
is Mr. Yan.

42:29.560 --> 42:31.680
The painter is Cui Jun.

42:33.640 --> 42:34.480
Who's Cui Jun?

42:36.480 --> 42:37.440
Maybe

42:38.680 --> 42:39.600
I can try something.

43:04.280 --> 43:05.320
Where did Wu Shiguang and Wangyan go?

43:05.400 --> 43:06.840
How did they disappear
in the blink of an eye?

43:08.360 --> 43:09.880
They've gone into the painting.

43:10.480 --> 43:11.360
Why did they leave me behind?

43:12.360 --> 43:13.280
What good would you do?

43:13.360 --> 43:14.880
What good would I do?

43:14.960 --> 43:15.800
I figured it out already.

43:17.120 --> 43:19.320
The girl in the painting
is Little Pomegranate.

43:19.400 --> 43:21.800
And this story must have
something to do with Mr. Yan.

43:21.880 --> 43:23.520
As for the great demon,

43:24.040 --> 43:26.360
that's you, Han Ba!

43:27.240 --> 43:28.120
Am I right?

43:29.800 --> 43:31.040
Pretty sharp, aren't I?

43:32.640 --> 43:33.920
Good for you.

43:34.560 --> 43:36.000
You've figured out
what everyone already knows.

43:39.880 --> 43:41.280
Your story with Little Pomegranate

43:41.360 --> 43:42.800
must've been full of longing
and heartbreak.

43:43.520 --> 43:44.480
Come on, tell us already.

43:50.800 --> 43:53.000
My name is Su Jian. What's your name?

43:54.840 --> 43:56.200
Why won't you say anything?

43:56.280 --> 43:58.240
<i>You won't even tell me your name?</i>
